descriptionHtml:
Browse through brands that want to work with Instagram talent. Choose the brands you want to work with, post original content to your followers and get paid directly to your bank account. Exclusively for users with 1,000 Instagram followers or more.

EXPLORE BRANDS you love already or help new ones get exposure
- Your reward is based on Instagram reach and engagement
- No hidden fees or negotiation means full transparency
- You decide who to work with

POST A PHOTO

- £40 minimum payment – significant payouts for larger accounts

title: TAKUMI

creator: Takumi International Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Join the TAKUMI Creator Community!

The TAKUMI app is your one-stop campaign delivery system for creators and brands. Upon acceptance, creators can browse, apply, accept campaigns + briefs, and submit content for paid brand partnerships - and get paid directly to their bank account.

Apply for Acceptance
Create a profile and link social accounts. Our Community Management team will thoroughly review and measure your profile’s quality + social strength with our team of experts, as well as third party authentication platforms.

Explore Brands
Upon acceptance, you can browse current recruiting campaigns from some of the top global brands in beauty, consumer goods, food + bev, and many more.

Submit + Post Content
When onboarded to a campaign, your briefing materials + scope will be available in app, as well as your submission portals for the brand + your TAKUMI rep to review and approve for live

Get Paid
- Reward always visible in TAKUMI app
- Direct deposit to your bank account
- Guaranteed rewards for on-brief content
- No hidden fees
descriptionShort: The TAKUMI app is your one-stop campaign delivery system for creators and brands

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Its all about making lives easier!
And in this update we added the option to easily logout from the current logged in account after you've requested for that account to be deleted.
Enjoy :-)
